    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/3a03db8ffd3901cae8d99522eefcf61b.poster.avif?t=1768890418\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/3a03db8ffd3901cae8d99522eefcf61b.webm?t=1768890418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/3a03db8ffd3901cae8d99522eefcf61b.mp4?t=1768890418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剧情丰富、基于社交联结的RPG游戏，融合了角色连段招式与JRPG元素。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到云之镇：世界上唯一拥有魔法的城镇。</strong>被迫置身于新环境的你，将与一群意想不到的伙伴一同踏上旅程，揭开这个独一无二之地的秘密与伤痕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/75cd6a2e1d8deefae98e6e6fea194a6c.avif?t=1768890418\" width=620 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >云之镇是聚集了许多年轻魔法师的魔法城镇。在白天探索城镇，与周围的人互相交流，以获得更强大的力量。发展你的人际关系并建立社交联结，就能解锁新能力、升级和各种武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/8247c14c5f029a6402f344d81c94448c.poster.avif?t=1768890418\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/8247c14c5f029a6402f344d81c94448c.webm?t=1768890418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/8247c14c5f029a6402f344d81c94448c.mp4?t=1768890418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>体验刺激的角色招式战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >到了夜晚，世界间的界限将变得模糊。前往城镇边缘，与满怀复仇心的精灵战斗，探索隐藏的文明与失落的传说。借由华丽的连段角色动作，将敌人打向空中、冲刺穿越他们，展现你的帅气战斗风格。挥舞刀剑、锁链、拳头等武器击败你的敌人。尝试各种被动/主动能力、自定义模组与技能，让战斗更加丰富多变。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/5b995f8b9780cf1bb1248c6fd46e66e1.poster.avif?t=1768890418\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/5b995f8b9780cf1bb1248c6fd46e66e1.webm?t=1768890418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/5b995f8b9780cf1bb1248c6fd46e66e1.mp4?t=1768890418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>活力充沛的生动世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《SONZAI：神在之地》采用优美的水墨极简艺术风格，搭配精心制作的动画（每一帧均为手绘），借此讲述发人深省的故事，探讨存在、个性，以及&quot;特别&quot;的真正意义。在这个充满隐藏传说的广阔世界中，你如何与SONZAI丰富多彩的角色交流，参与他们的人生故事，或许将改变一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/4498c47bf0de3664bba80fec1049f301.avif?t=1768890418\" width=620 height=156 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索广阔的世界──例如云之镇旁的燃烧小镇，或是地底的失落文明。每个新区域都有其独特的美学与居民。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前往&quot;牛乳铺&quot;喝杯珍珠奶茶、聊聊八卦，或是当个好心人，到孤儿院当志愿者。留意你与谁交好、与谁疏远：每个角色都有自己的人生与故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解角色喜爱的活动，精进相关能力，与周围的人变得更亲近。随着关系有所进展，将解锁新能力、升级等内容！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合帅气的连段系统、华丽战斗效果与角色招式的战斗体验──驾驭多种武器，搭配被动或主动符文能力与特技，看看你能以多酷炫的方式击败敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >造访安雅的商店，组合获得的掉落物与符文，制作具有多种特技的模组，提升你的战斗实力至新境界。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380980/extras/52e7494b8520971e61b604b31200c203.avif?t=1768890418\" width=606 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未知的机会与新朋友正等待着你。《SONZAI：神在之地》是来自印度加尔各答的2人创新游戏团队&quot;2 Odd Diodes&quot;的首款作品，由Top Hat Studios、松竹、Game Bridge联合发行。</p>",
